rules.ruleString: Must have passed 3 (I/W) units in {MED1011, MED1022, MED2031}
Must be enrolled in course version {4531, 4533, M6011, M6019}

description: MED2000 provides an overall result for Year 1 & 2 MBBS based upon achievement in MED1011, MED1022, MED2031, MED2042 and the first Integrated Vertical Assessment (VIA) examination. Students will need to successfully complete MED1011, MED1022, MED2031, MED2042 and the VIA examination. A grade will be awarded for MED2000 which is based on student achievement in MED1011, MED1022, MED2031 and MED2042 and the VIA examination.
faculty: Faculty of Medicine, Nursing and Health Sciences
